HEADWORD: Redthroat
<hw>Red"throat`</hw> <pr>(r?d"thr?t`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A small Australian singing bird
(<spn>Phyrrholaemus brunneus</spn>). The upper parts are brown, the
center of the throat red.</def>⟦br⟧
